Usage: dbSchema [-help] [[<objNamePattern> [<objAttrNamePattern>]] | [-parent <objNamePatternForParent> [-list ]]]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
<objNamePattern>                      # Object Name or Pattern
                                      # (string, optional)
<objAttrNamePattern>                  # Object Attribute Name or Pattern
                                      # (string, optional)
-list                                 # To print as a list of parent objects
                                      # (bool, optional)
-parent <objNamePatternForParent>     # Type of Object/Attribute for which
                                      # parent needs to be found
                                      # (string, optional)